hod`\n  - `invokeExactMethod`\n  - `invokeStaticMethod`\n  - `invokeExactStaticMethod`\n  - `getAccessibleMethod`\n  - `getAccessibleMethodFromInterfaceNest`\n  - `getAccessibleMethodFromSuperclass`\n  - `getMatchingAccessibleMethod` direct lookup\n  - `getMatchingAccessibleMethod` public-method scan fallback\n- Disabled MethodUtils method caching before each test to ensure dynamic-access call sites are reached reliably.\n- Made the existing top-level placeholder test class public:\n  - `Commons_beanutils_coreTest.java`\n\nPer instruction, I did not run compilation or tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_055da6fec84f077e0169f777b617b08194bc34fc9ae20feefc\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1590, "output": 1240, "cacheRead": 29184, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32014, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777825702908, "responseId": "resp_055da6fec84f077e0169f777a75b488194a8913a4356d8da93"}, "toolResults": []}
